HEADWORD: Expos
<hw>Ex`po`s⟦eacute⟧"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.,
prop. p. p. of <ets>exposer</ets>. See <er>Expose</er>, <pos>v.
t.</pos>]</ety> <def>A formal recital or exposition of facts; exposure,
or revelation, of something which some one wished to keep
concealed.</def>⟦br⟧
